{"tid":446673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 日本最可愛女高中生選拔 各縣代表一覽","createTime":"2017-10-24T13:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T16:53:10.000Z","uid":45646,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3abc814667bc2f7f6be060cf5064b0b38aa9883a","tid":446673,"uid":45646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"又到了一年一度「日本最可愛女高中生」選舉的時候啦！本屆選舉如同往常分成北海道・東北、關東、中部、關西、中國・四國、九州・沖縄6個地區，47個都道府縣先前已透過選舉選出各自的代表來角逐后冠，沒想到比賽才剛開始沒多久，秋田縣代表就被酸民攻擊到崩潰，不僅宣布退賽，連推特帳號都一併刪除了，逼得主辦單位不得出來滅火，呼籲大家「留點口德」。<br />\n<br />\n「突然覺得有點可憐，是誰幫她報名的？」結果秋田代表退賽消息被轉po到台灣《批踢踢實業坊》，部份鄉民竟也十分認同日本酸民的意見，「人要有自知之明」、「長這樣也敢來選？有沒有羞恥心啊」、「醜死了，這是選美比賽，不是說謊大賽」、「本來覺得這樣說別人外貌怎樣很不好，點進去一看......。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g6oqa5sr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg6oqa5sr&h=0df68f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒想到比賽才剛開始沒多久，秋田縣代表就被酸民攻擊到崩潰。翻攝官方網站<br />\n<br />\n其它代表：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u0xq52jr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu0xq52jr&h=99bca514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/560puhvg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F560puhvg&h=c0c3eefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dtph1mr9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdtph1mr9&h=acab0c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/co529jry\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fco529jry&h=bfc3ecab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4kn3gvmd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4kn3gvmd&h=9c3d8458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171022/1226787/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171022%2F1226787%2F&d=zI7nI0FtvnPeIT9ky4u6pbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=04e03b00\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171022/1226787/</a><br />\n<br />\n岡山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55e71a818592c5862071fbb748ed303e3655d41","tid":446673,"uid":6294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"福島縣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed347ca92ce7223bab8f18e274f58985850b47","tid":446673,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"見到第一張相即時比負皮"},{"pid":"522d4d6dd39d7a8d5fc1a2fe8ae333fbe8bf0853","tid":446673,"uid":119027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"琦玉 新瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53512f94d43990a9377cf13742db71e3785dfdba","tid":446673,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"秋田縣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cef26efafc53df8e88f3ce747c822e7ee430415","tid":446673,"uid":144373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"福島 山梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70920dc804efcc59353fcc347fe87119b8891937","tid":446673,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"新潟 岐阜 鳥取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef38559d84cf07f874b895655721d010ae0375dd","tid":446673,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"埼玉win"},{"pid":"cc1c64385227ec2